Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.57,0:00:15.41,main,15,0,0,0,,Almost done. Let's gang up and end it in one.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.75,0:00:24.21,main,390,0,0,0,,What is this? Gross!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.21,0:00:25.58,main,556,0,0,0,,It's all sticky!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.57,0:00:27.33,main,196,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.33,0:00:28.61,main,Z2,0,0,0,,It doesn't hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.61,0:00:30.84,main,556,0,0,0,,Yeah, seems fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.84,0:00:33.01,main,390,0,0,0,,So it's just for show?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.01,0:00:36.05,main,390,0,0,0,,How dare you spew this \Ndisgusting gunk all over us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.05,0:00:38.22,main,15,0,0,0,,Let's try it again, guys. Stick to the plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.47,0:00:42.14,main,666,0,0,0,,What the heck?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.53,0:00:44.07,main,214,0,0,0,,K-Kokoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.67,0:00:58.99,main,390,0,0,0,,Why are you spacing out, Zorome?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.50,0:01:01.46,main,390,0,0,0,,Hey, you listening to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.46,0:01:04.00,main,666,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah. It's nothing, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.00,0:01:05.42,main,556,0,0,0,,Futoshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.27,0:01:08.00,main,214,0,0,0,,Don't worry. It's nothing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.14,0:01:12.45,main,15,0,0,0,,Focus. We're in the middle of a battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.45,0:01:14.13,main,56,0,0,0,,I-I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.30,0:01:20.07,main,Z2,0,0,0,,Let's finish it off, darling!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.07,0:01:22.01,main,16,0,0,0,,Huh? Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.79,0:01:39.07,main,Z2,0,0,0,,Darling?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.58,0:01:41.08,main,16,0,0,0,,This is bad, Zero Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.08,0:01:42.56,main,16,0,0,0,,It's gonna be exposed!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.56,0:01:43.83,italics,666214,0,0,0,,Don't tell her, dumbass!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.87,0:01:51.17,main,390,0,0,0,,My parasite suit!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.77,0:02:02.31,italics,,0,0,0,,Come to me, as our inhibitions crumble
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.83,0:02:07.50,italics,,0,0,0,,Please don't fear me
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.73,0:02:21.49,italics,,0,0,0,,The flightless bird dreams of a sky
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.22,0:02:28.37,italics,,0,0,0,,Whose colors blend into \Nthe wrong shade of red
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.34,0:02:37.16,italics,,0,0,0,,I tried to block out the banging on my door
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.16,0:02:43.72,italics,,0,0,0,,Are you one banging on it? \NOr is it someone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.10,0:02:50.00,italics,,0,0,0,,Will your lips taste the kiss of death?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.00,0:02:57.23,italics,,0,0,0,,Darling, our destiny \Ncourses through our veins
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.61,0:03:03.99,italics,,0,0,0,,A change is sweeping across \Nthe world... Is it love?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.83,0:03:13.25,italics,,0,0,0,,I want us to come together \Nmore than anyone, darling
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.57,0:03:17.99,italics,,0,0,0,,Please don't fear me
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.59,0:03:21.19,italics,,0,0,0,,Kiss me now
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.57,0:03:31.48,main,56,0,0,0,,You've got the wrong idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.48,0:03:37.66,main,56,0,0,0,,We only didn't tell you because we didn't \Nwant to distract you during the battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.66,0:03:38.57,main,214,0,0,0,,As for me,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.57,0:03:41.81,main,214,0,0,0,,I simply found you amazingly \Nbeautiful, Kokoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.81,0:03:44.19,main,214,0,0,0,,Believe me! This is straight from the heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.50,0:03:49.04,main,326,0,0,0,,So stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.02,0:03:53.87,main,666,0,0,0,,Y'know, it's not like being \Nseen hurts you or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.87,0:03:55.99,main,390,0,0,0,,Excuse me? What did you just say?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.99,0:03:56.92,main,16,0,0,0,,Wait, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.92,0:04:01.26,main,16,0,0,0,,Zero Two told me that parasites are, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.14,0:04:05.01,main,16,0,0,0,,better off being a little pervy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.01,0:04:07.09,main,16,0,0,0,,Right, Zero Two?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.09,0:04:08.39,main,Z2,0,0,0,,Yup, yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.29,0:04:10.14,main,15,0,0,0,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.42,0:04:18.29,main,390,0,0,0,,I can't believe they've been ogling us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.29,0:04:21.76,main,390,0,0,0,,Wait, were they doing it \Nback at the beach, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.76,0:04:23.65,main,196,0,0,0,,That's how boys are.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.65,0:04:26.16,main,390,0,0,0,,Unbelievable! They're such creeps!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.51,0:04:29.09,main,15,0,0,0,,And here I thought we'd finally \Nstarted to link up well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.71,0:04:32.04,main,15,0,0,0,,This is a matter that can \Ndeeply affect squad morale.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.50,0:04:35.00,main,556,0,0,0,,All of you need to calm down a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.00,0:04:38.92,main,390,0,0,0,,I've had it! I don't wanna be \Nanywhere near the boys anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.31,0:04:41.80,main,390,0,0,0,,I know what to do. We should quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.80,0:04:43.92,main,390,0,0,0,,Let's put an end to our communal \Nlife with the boys!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.68,0:04:53.06,sign_6970_50_Bath_and_Changin,Sign,0,0,0,,Bath and Changing Area\NNo Boys Allowed!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.94,0:04:57.37,main,390,0,0,0,,Listen up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.83,0:05:00.31,main,390,0,0,0,,Boys are banned from \Nsetting foot on this side.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.31,0:05:03.87,main,666,0,0,0,,Wh-Who died and made you \Nthe boss? This is messed up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.87,0:05:04.89,main,390,0,0,0,,Zorome.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.65,0:05:09.03,main,390,0,0,0,,Cross that line, and you will regret it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.93,0:05:16.91,italics,Fra,0,0,0,,Ah, puberty.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.46,0:05:22.67,main,8,0,0,0,,It's unprecedented for so many members \Nof a squad to hit puberty at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.67,0:05:27.68,main,7,0,0,0,,Statistics indicate that it has always \Nbeen at most one or two together.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.00,0:05:30.46,main,8,0,0,0,,But this time, it's practically everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.46,0:05:32.10,main,8,0,0,0,,It's clearly an abnormal case.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.68,0:05:35.60,italics,Fra,0,0,0,,But that's what makes it so intriguing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.60,0:05:41.48,main,7,0,0,0,,If we go by APE's manual, we should \Nintervene and resolve the issue immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.38,0:05:46.32,italics,Fra,0,0,0,,Listen to yourself. What would be the \Npoint of this test team if we did that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.09,0:05:50.77,italics,Fra,0,0,0,,Just observe what happens and \Ngive me detailed reports.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.22,0:05:56.33,italics,Fra,0,0,0,,Don't you dare interfere \Nor let the geezers know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.08,0:06:01.83,main,390,0,0,0,,Did you see the look on the \Nboys' faces back there?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.83,0:06:03.66,main,390,0,0,0,,Serves them right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.93,0:06:06.97,main,196,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.10,0:06:15.27,main,390,0,0,0,,Now we've just gotta rein her in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.44,0:06:23.28,main,390,0,0,0,,H-Hey, what do you think you're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.28,0:06:26.48,main,666,0,0,0,,Well, seeing as we can't use the \Nbath, we took a dip in the lake.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.48,0:06:28.41,main,666,0,0,0,,It felt amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.41,0:06:30.41,main,390,0,0,0,,W-Would it kill you to get dressed?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.41,0:06:32.26,main,390,0,0,0,,Are you listening to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.26,0:06:35.91,main,666,0,0,0,,What we do in our territory \Nis none of your damn business.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.42,0:06:45.42,main,390,0,0,0,,What was that all about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.83,0:06:47.70,main,196,0,0,0,,They're trying to provoke us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.70,0:06:49.31,main,16,0,0,0,,I bet it was Goro's idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.74,0:06:53.14,main,16,0,0,0,,Zorome and Futoshi couldn't \Nhave thought of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.58,0:06:57.85,main,390,0,0,0,,They get to have fun in the lake, \Nand we're stuck cleaning the bath?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.85,0:06:59.02,main,390,0,0,0,,It's not fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.02,0:07:01.30,main,556,0,0,0,,We can't really complain about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.30,0:07:05.73,main,196,0,0,0,,We're the ones who declared \Nthe bath off-limits to the boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.73,0:07:07.91,main,390,0,0,0,,I know, but still!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.91,0:07:13.18,main,390,0,0,0,,Man, why must cleaning be the only \Nthing we have to do ourselves?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.18,0:07:18.54,main,390,0,0,0,,I wish the invisible caretakers would handle it, \Nlike they do with our food and laundry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.21,0:07:26.04,main,56,0,0,0,,Sorry, but we've taken over this area.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.04,0:07:29.17,main,56,0,0,0,,We noticed that you girls \Nhadn't taped it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.45,0:07:33.68,main,666,0,0,0,,So good!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.68,0:07:36.56,main,666,0,0,0,,Today's breakfast is extraordinary!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.56,0:07:38.60,main,390,0,0,0,,No fair! You're heartless!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.60,0:07:40.23,main,56,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.23,0:07:45.81,main,56,0,0,0,,So what say we both drop all the \Nsilly rules and eat together?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.73,0:07:47.54,main,196,0,0,0,,It's a trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.54,0:07:48.67,main,16,0,0,0,,Agreed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.67,0:07:50.03,main,16,0,0,0,,Don't go, Miku!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.41,0:08:00.87,main,390,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.06,0:08:03.59,main,56,0,0,0,,Talk about pigheaded.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.07,0:08:07.38,main,16,0,0,0,,Everyone's gotten too stubborn about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.78,0:08:11.39,main,16,0,0,0,,This is looking really bad. We need\Nto hurry up and do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.91,0:08:13.67,main,Z2,0,0,0,,Is that how you feel, darling?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.71,0:08:16.13,main,Z2,0,0,0,,I'm the opposite.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.43,0:08:19.72,main,Z2,0,0,0,,I think it could use a \Nlittle spicing up, in fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.59,0:08:37.62,main,556,0,0,0,,Could it be you have an interest in plants?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.62,0:08:38.78,main,326,0,0,0,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.78,0:08:40.43,main,556,0,0,0,,Then why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.43,0:08:44.66,main,326,0,0,0,,This place is the perfect getaway \Nwhen I want to be alone. That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.98,0:08:51.89,main,556,0,0,0,,I begged Nana to let me take \Ncare of this greenhouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.89,0:08:56.18,main,556,0,0,0,,We had seeds, so I've been planting and \Ngrowing them while studying up on things.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.73,0:09:00.86,main,556,0,0,0,,Have you ever heard of \Nthe language of flowers?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.86,0:09:05.06,main,556,0,0,0,,This is a hibiscus. Its floral \Nmeaning is "delicate beauty."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.93,0:09:09.21,main,556,0,0,0,,And the cattleya over \Nthere stands for "alluring."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.03,0:09:17.75,main,556,0,0,0,,Hey, do you really not mind \Nchatting with me like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.75,0:09:19.35,main,326,0,0,0,,Are you talking about the fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.35,0:09:22.67,main,326,0,0,0,,It's stupid. I can't be bothered to play along.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.67,0:09:25.09,main,556,0,0,0,,Really? That's so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.09,0:09:26.08,main,326,0,0,0,,Cool?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.08,0:09:30.83,main,556,0,0,0,,It takes a lot of courage \Nto refuse to toe the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.57,0:09:33.55,main,556,0,0,0,,I was too scared to say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.86,0:09:38.18,sign_13831_120_Your_First_Child,Sign,0,0,0,,Your First Childbirth\N{\fs12\c&H8FB1D2&}— What's Best for Your Baby —
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.01,0:09:42.81,main,326,0,0,0,,You brought it back with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.25,0:09:44.60,main,556,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.24,0:09:49.10,main,326,0,0,0,,Not that it matters to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.43,0:10:02.84,main,390,0,0,0,,I'm starving.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.84,0:10:03.86,main,196,0,0,0,,And whose fault is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.86,0:10:07.83,main,390,0,0,0,,Hey, that's why I'm looking \Nfor things to eat, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.25,0:10:12.97,main,390,0,0,0,,So this is what the first floor's like.\NI've never come here before.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.66,0:10:19.04,main,15,0,0,0,,It's sealed off.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.04,0:10:21.34,main,390,0,0,0,,Nobody's using it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.65,0:10:26.35,main,15,0,0,0,,How long will this fight go on?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.35,0:10:30.85,main,196,0,0,0,,Well... I wouldn't mind if \Nthings stayed this way forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.98,0:10:34.98,main,Z2,0,0,0,,I taste a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.75,0:10:36.90,main,196,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.82,0:10:39.79,main,15,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.74,0:10:43.53,main,390,0,0,0,,Whose side are you on?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.09,0:10:46.42,main,15,0,0,0,,We'd like you to cooperate, if you could.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.07,0:10:51.21,main,Z2,0,0,0,,What you're doing is lame. \NYou're just playing around.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.21,0:10:53.70,main,390,0,0,0,,Wha... You don't know that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.51,0:10:57.01,main,15,0,0,0,,Believe it or not, we're serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.01,0:10:58.38,main,556,0,0,0,,H-Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.38,0:11:00.55,main,Z2,0,0,0,,You're serious, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.82,0:11:06.26,main,Z2,0,0,0,,All right. I'll join you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.27,0:11:10.79,sign_15999_143_Bath_and_Changin,Sign,0,0,0,,Bath and Changing Area\NNo Boys Allowed!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.99,0:11:12.58,main,666,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.58,0:11:13.48,main,214,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.48,0:11:15.42,main,Z2,0,0,0,,They said you can use the bath now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.24,0:11:19.88,sign_16262_147_Girls_Bathing,Sign,0,0,0,,Girls Bathing
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.26,0:11:21.20,sign_16262_147_Girls_Bathing,Sign,0,0,0,,Boys Bathing
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.45,0:11:28.45,sign_16262_147_Girls_Bathing,Sign,0,0,0,,Boys Bathing
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.09,0:11:28.45,main,16,0,0,0,,Zero Two said it was okay \Nfor us to use the bath?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.58,0:11:30.45,main,16,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.45,0:11:34.59,main,666,0,0,0,,Really. The girls must've \Nwaved the white flag.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.70,0:11:53.34,main,56,0,0,0,,Wait! I-It's not what it looks like!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.44,0:11:57.27,main,666,0,0,0,,Hear us out! It was Zero Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.69,0:12:00.41,main,56,0,0,0,,Crap. We can't stop them now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.35,0:12:07.66,main,16,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.66,0:12:12.12,main,16,0,0,0,,Why would you do this, Zero Two?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.12,0:12:16.63,main,Z2,0,0,0,,This is a real fight. Come at \Nme with all you've got, darling.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.22,0:12:29.14,main,214,0,0,0,,We were set up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.14,0:12:30.77,main,15,0,0,0,,Enough excuses!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.66,0:12:35.73,main,16,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.94,0:12:42.49,main,Z2,0,0,0,,Hurry up and catch me if you can, darling!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.10,0:12:45.61,main,16,0,0,0,,You're on!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.61,0:12:47.42,main,390,0,0,0,,Perverts! You horny perverts!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.42,0:12:49.49,main,390,0,0,0,,Fiends! I'm gonna break you in half!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.49,0:12:51.37,main,56,0,0,0,,We should leave for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.37,0:12:53.46,main,214,0,0,0,,Hey, our clothes are gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.46,0:12:54.87,main,666,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.31,0:13:10.89,main,16,0,0,0,,This is it. There's nowhere\Nleft for you to run—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.73,0:13:16.77,main,Z2,0,0,0,,Darling, you pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.16,0:13:38.57,main,16,0,0,0,,Why'd you do this, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.98,0:13:43.67,main,Z2,0,0,0,,The fight. I wanted to try \Ntaking part in a human fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.94,0:13:46.13,main,16,0,0,0,,Zero Two...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.98,0:13:51.91,main,Z2,0,0,0,,Hey, darling, do I seem \Na little more human now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.41,0:13:57.89,main,16,0,0,0,,Zero Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.59,0:14:16.75,main,666,0,0,0,,That's it! We've had it with this crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.75,0:14:18.71,main,390,0,0,0,,We're the ones running out of patience!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.04,0:14:21.84,main,666,0,0,0,,Shut up! Don't look down on us boys!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.84,0:14:24.67,main,390,0,0,0,,Why don't {\i1}you{\i0} try sparing \Na thought for us girls?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.67,0:14:26.57,main,666,0,0,0,,Shut up! All of you—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.57,0:14:28.72,main,7,0,0,0,,Knock it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.22,0:14:36.97,main,7,0,0,0,,What were you going to do if \Nklaxosaurs attacked right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.30,0:14:41.50,main,7,0,0,0,,Can you really sortie like this? \NI certainly don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.50,0:14:46.36,main,8,0,0,0,,You're parasites. Don't forget \Nwhat comes first and foremost.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.75,0:14:48.81,main,All,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.85,0:14:54.34,main,7,0,0,0,,Could they be any more \Nunlike the other children?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.83,0:14:58.25,main,8,0,0,0,,I wasn't expecting Zero Two to join in, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.23,0:15:00.75,main,Z2,0,0,0,,I had so much fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.12,0:15:04.00,main,Z2,0,0,0,,I loved how naughty and rebellious that was!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.40,0:15:07.31,main,15,0,0,0,,What were you thinking? Explain yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.73,0:15:11.95,main,Z2,0,0,0,,If you keep half-assing things like that, \Nyou'll end up like the adults one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.01,0:15:17.93,main,Z2,0,0,0,,If you have anything you wanna say, \Nyou'd better spit it out while you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.33,0:15:25.52,main,Z2,0,0,0,,Because you're all going \Nto die sooner or later.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.02,0:15:34.33,main,666,0,0,0,,I'm so pissed off!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.33,0:15:37.41,main,666,0,0,0,,Why are the girls so condescending, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.14,0:15:40.88,main,326,0,0,0,,They look down on us boys, obviously.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.88,0:15:44.17,main,666,0,0,0,,Nobody asked for a calm \Nand composed analysis!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.17,0:15:46.90,main,666,0,0,0,,Damn it. Screw it, I'm done.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.90,0:15:48.73,main,666,0,0,0,,I'm through with the girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.83,0:15:54.89,main,16,0,0,0,,I feel bad saying this, but I \Nthought that was kind of fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.89,0:15:55.72,main,666,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.42,0:16:00.38,main,16,0,0,0,,Zero Two was laughing her heart out,\Nlike she was enjoying herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.19,0:16:06.44,main,16,0,0,0,,I'd never spared much thought \Nfor how girls felt before now...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.44,0:16:10.94,main,666,0,0,0,,Why bother? They're weirdo whack jobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.43,0:16:13.51,main,16,0,0,0,,Yeah, I don't get them at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.98,0:16:17.45,main,16,0,0,0,,But that's exactly why I started \Nwanting to know more about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.93,0:16:22.09,main,16,0,0,0,,That way, I might be able \Nto offer her more support.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.55,0:16:26.46,main,326,0,0,0,,If you're talking about Zero Two, \Nyou're barking up the wrong tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.46,0:16:30.50,main,326,0,0,0,,She's the ultimate pistil.\NShe doesn't need your support.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.97,0:16:33.34,main,16,0,0,0,,No, Zero Two is a normal girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.70,0:16:35.13,main,16,0,0,0,,And it's not just her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.65,0:16:39.69,main,16,0,0,0,,Pistils let us stamens \Nhandle all the controls,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.69,0:16:44.73,main,16,0,0,0,,but their frail bodies are the ones \Nbearing the brunt of each battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.73,0:16:48.45,main,214,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah. That must be rough.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.07,0:16:52.61,main,16,0,0,0,,Even so, they connect to the \NFRANXX and do their best,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.01,0:16:54.90,main,16,0,0,0,,placing all their trust in us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.25,0:16:58.73,main,16,0,0,0,,Watching her like that \Nreally made me think...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.94,0:17:04.75,main,16,0,0,0,,I want to be stronger and \Ntake better care of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.93,0:17:10.00,main,56,0,0,0,,Well, the girls are always \Ngiving it their all in battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.63,0:17:13.63,main,56,0,0,0,,And if we ogle them while they are...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.98,0:17:16.38,main,214,0,0,0,,Of course they'd hate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.21,0:17:20.38,main,666,0,0,0,,Hey, I'm a man, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.38,0:17:24.14,main,666,0,0,0,,Even I feel the need to look after \Nmy partner and take care of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.71,0:17:28.78,main,666,0,0,0,,And I don't wanna see any \Nof them in pain, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.31,0:17:32.27,main,56,0,0,0,,That means there's only \None thing for us to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.33,0:17:36.02,main,15,0,0,0,,"Die sooner or later," huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.37,0:17:43.93,main,556,0,0,0,,H-Hey, you know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.99,0:17:47.33,main,556,0,0,0,,I really think this can't go on!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.33,0:17:53.02,main,556,0,0,0,,There are things that we can't do alone, \Nbut can do if we work with the boys!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.02,0:17:56.09,main,556,0,0,0,,And there are lots of things \Nlike that, aren't there?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.09,0:17:58.34,main,556,0,0,0,,Piloting the FRANXX is one of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.93,0:18:05.35,main,556,0,0,0,,Yeah, the boys are perverts, and I have \Nno idea what goes through their heads.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.35,0:18:10.35,main,556,0,0,0,,Boys and girls are nothing alike, but that's \Nwhy it's good for us to be together!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.69,0:18:15.94,main,556,0,0,0,,After all, that's how... \Nuh... it's born, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.45,0:18:20.14,main,556,0,0,0,,You know, like... the future, hope, and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.65,0:18:23.45,main,556,0,0,0,,So... so...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.82,0:18:27.27,main,15,0,0,0,,It's really unusual for \Nyou to be so assertive.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.27,0:18:29.46,main,196,0,0,0,,Yeah, it surprised me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.09,0:18:33.57,main,15,0,0,0,,What you said did sting, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.21,0:18:38.38,main,196,0,0,0,,We can't just be the ones who \Ncomplain all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.38,0:18:42.14,main,390,0,0,0,,W-Wait a second! Are you \Nthinking of forgiving the boys?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.14,0:18:45.06,main,15,0,0,0,,Well, we won't get anywhere as things stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.18,0:18:48.48,main,390,0,0,0,,Oh, really? Suit yourselves, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.95,0:18:51.98,main,390,0,0,0,,I'm not letting this go, \Neven if I'm left all alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.98,0:18:53.49,main,556,0,0,0,,Wait, Miku!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.53,0:18:57.46,main,666,0,0,0,,I'm not gonna beg and plead \Nfor forgiveness, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.46,0:18:59.34,main,56,0,0,0,,You're still going on about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.49,0:19:01.65,main,15,0,0,0,,Goro...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.17,0:19:04.74,main,15,0,0,0,,Miku's missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.74,0:19:06.98,main,15,0,0,0,,Please help us find her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.98,0:19:08.00,main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.65,0:19:11.29,main,214,0,0,0,,Miku! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.01,0:19:09.88,main,556,0,0,0,,Miku!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.88,0:19:10.28,main,196,0,0,0,,Miku!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.28,0:19:12.22,main,666,0,0,0,,Hey, Miku!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.37,0:19:12.22,main,15,0,0,0,,Miku?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.22,0:19:13.00,main,Someone,0,0,0,,Miku!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.71,0:19:16.00,main,666,0,0,0,,Come on out!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.00,0:19:17.47,main,Someone,0,0,0,,Miku!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.51,0:19:22.45,main,390,0,0,0,,Listen to that. They've all made up already.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.61,0:19:26.77,main,390,0,0,0,,Well, I'm still not leaving this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.56,0:19:44.83,main,390,0,0,0,,Is this...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.73,0:19:49.73,main,390,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.26,0:20:04.26,main,556,0,0,0,,Miku!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.34,0:20:08.60,main,556,0,0,0,,Thank goodness. We were so worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.93,0:20:10.11,main,556,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.17,0:20:13.35,main,16,0,0,0,,What's this room?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.35,0:20:17.75,main,Z2,0,0,0,,Probably one of the rooms the \Nformer Squad 13 parasites used.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.31,0:20:19.17,main,326,0,0,0,,Former...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.81,0:20:21.61,main,196,0,0,0,,...Squad 13?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.61,0:20:29.15,main,56,0,0,0,,Oh, of course this plantation had a defensive \Nsquad before we were assigned here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.06,0:20:33.62,main,666,0,0,0,,So how come they aren't here now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.30,0:20:35.98,main,666,0,0,0,,Why's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.38,0:20:39.63,main,Z2,0,0,0,,They were wiped out, obviously.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.30,0:20:44.14,main,15,0,0,0,,They couldn't come back alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.23,0:20:56.07,main,56,0,0,0,,We won't survive unless we all \Nget to know each other better.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.54,0:21:00.09,main,56,0,0,0,,Let's make up, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.53,0:21:04.57,main,666,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.35,0:21:08.43,main,666,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, okay? I apologize!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.31,0:21:13.70,main,666,0,0,0,,I'll try my best not to leer at you anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.18,0:21:17.02,main,390,0,0,0,,I bet you'll fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.73,0:21:21.53,main,390,0,0,0,,I'm way too cute, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.22,0:21:27.51,main,390,0,0,0,,So you can do it a little, \Nbut don't take it too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.10,0:21:30.86,main,,0,0,0,,O-Okay, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.23,0:21:40.31,italics,390,0,0,0,,The vase by the window had lilacs in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.15,0:21:48.78,italics,390,0,0,0,,What were the former Squad 13 parasites \Nthinking when they placed them there?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.61,0:21:52.06,italics,390,0,0,0,,There's no way for us to find out now,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.99,0:21:59.14,italics,390,0,0,0,,but the next day, we went back and \Nreplaced them with fresh lilacs.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.51,0:22:08.13,italics,390,0,0,0,,In the language of flowers, lilacs represent \Nfriendship, fond memories, and youth.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.09,0:22:14.86,main,390,0,0,0,,Would you cut it out?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.86,0:22:16.12,main,666,0,0,0,,I didn't do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.12,0:22:17.85,main,390,0,0,0,,You were ogling me again, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.85,0:22:18.69,main,666,0,0,0,,I was not!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.69,0:22:20.01,main,390,0,0,0,,Ugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.15,0:22:33.70,main,16,0,0,0,,Zero Two, I want you to speak \Nyour mind with me from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.70,0:22:36.83,main,Z2,0,0,0,,Oh? Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.54,0:22:40.58,main,16,0,0,0,,Because I want to get to know you better.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.53,0:22:48.27,main,Z2,0,0,0,,Darling... Grab on to me \Nand never let go, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.97,0:22:50.97,sign_33134_360_Episode_1,Title,0,0,0,,Episode 8
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.97,0:22:50.97,sign_33134_361_Alone_and_Loneso,Title,0,0,0,,Boys x Girls
